import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; function ImageGallery() { useEffect(() => { // Get the carousel element const carousel = document.querySelector('.carousel'); // Define the interval (in milliseconds) const interval = 2000; // Define a function to advance the carousel const advanceCarousel = () => { const currentIndex = Array.from(carousel.querySelectorAll('.carousel-item')).findIndex(item => item.classNameList.contains('active')); const nextIndex = currentIndex === carousel.childElementCount - 1 ? 0 : currentIndex + 1; // Trigger the carousel to slide to the next index carousel.querySelector(`.carousel-item:nth-child(${nextIndex + 1})`).classNameList.add('active'); carousel.querySelector(`.carousel-item:nth-child(${currentIndex + 1})`).classNameList.remove('active'); }; // Start the carousel interval const carouselInterval = setInterval(advanceCarousel, interval); // Clear the interval when the component unmounts return () => clearInterval(carouselInterval); }, []); return ( <>
